name: The nap sun
description:
This is an artwork from Serie: "What was left of Summer" and it was exhibited in an individual show at "Vocación Humana" Foundation in Buenos Aires, Argentina between October and November 2019.

Summer as a catalyst of sensations and emotions: the memory of a chilhood not so distant, the sound of the sea, a walk along the shore or just floating...

Aníbal Argañaraz
5611 x 4004 px
